14:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Murakkab foizlar kalkulyatori avval hisoblangan foizlarga foiz hisoblash — kapitalizatsiyani hisobga olgan holda kapitalning o'sishini ko'rsatadi. Formula: FV = PV × (1 + r/n)^(n×t), bunda PV — boshlang'ich summa, r — yillik stavka, n — kapitalizatsiya chastotasi (oylik uchun 12, choraklik 4, yillik 1), t — yillardagi muddat. Murakkab foizlar — uzoq muddatli investitsiyalash va jamg'arishning asosi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekiston banklarida (2025–2026) so'mdagi omonat stavkalari yillik 20-26%, valyutada 4-7%. Bunday stavkalarda murakkab foizlar ulkan ta'sir beradi: 50 mln so'mlik omonat yillik 24% da 5 yilga oylik kapitalizatsiya bilan 163,4 mln gacha o'sadi (o'sish 226,9%), holbuki kapitalizatsiyasiz (oddiy foizlar) 110 mln bo'lardi (o'sish 120%). Farq — 53 mln so'mdan ortiq."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Kapitalizatsiya chastotasi daromadlilikka sezilarli ta'sir qiladi. Yillik 24% stavka va 5 yil muddatda: yillik kapitalizatsiya +193,2%; choraklik — +211,5%; oylik — +226,9%; kunlik — +231,8% beradi. Yillik va oylik kapitalizatsiya o'rtasidagi farq 33,7 foiz punktni tashkil etadi — 50 mln omonatda bu qo'shimcha 16,8 mln so'm."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Omonatdan haqiqiy daromadni baholash uchun inflyatsiyani hisobga olish kerak. O'zbekistonda 2025-yilda inflyatsiya taxminan 7,3% ni tashkil etadi. 24% omonatning real daromadliligi = 24% − 7,3% = yillik 16,7%. Shunga qaramay, bu inflyatsiyadan ancha yuqori va murakkab foizlar ta'sirni kuchaytiradi. Bunda jismoniy shaxslarning omonat daromadidan rezidentlar uchun 5% (norezidentlar uchun 10%) "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/jshshs","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"JShShS"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" ushlab qolinadi — bank foizlarni to'lashda soliqni avtomatik ravishda ushlab qoladi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Bizning murakkab foizlar kalkulyatorimiz boshlang'ich summa, yillik stavka, kapitalizatsiya chastotasi, muddat va oylik to'ldirishlarni kiritish va bir zumda yakuniy summa, umumiy daromad va oylar bo'yicha kapital o'sish jadvalini olish imkonini beradi. Jamg'armalarni rejalashtirish, omonatlarni solishtirish va investitsiyalarni baholash uchun foydalaning."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 space-y-6","children":["$L19",["$L1a"]]}],"$L1b","$L1c"]}]
